{"type": "article", "id": 8609, "title": "忘了马斯克的火星殖民吧，发射小卫星就够火爆了", "description": "火爆的原因是够便宜。", "date": "2015-04-17T08:56:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2493, "name": "火箭"}, {"id": 2295, "name": "卫星"}, {"id": 876, "name": "波音"}, {"id": 9033, "name": "Rocket Lab"}, {"id": 260, "name": "微软"}, {"id": 1842, "name": "维珍"}, {"id": 9046, "name": "Paul Allen"}, {"id": 9047, "name": "Richard Branson"}], "category": 4, "author": 43366, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605214005RYBH1FOacIT2jmhJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.wired.com/2012/10/ff-elon-musk-qa/\" target=\"_blank\">2026 </a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.wired.com/2012/10/ff-elon-musk-qa/\" target=\"_blank\">年前在火星上建立第一个殖民地</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，这是 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">SpaceX </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">创始人 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Elon Musk </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">念叨了多年的计划，具体来说就是造出适合火星之旅的发动机、实现火箭回收再利用技术以降低成本，然后，出发。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t尽管 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">SpaceX </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的猎户座 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">9 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号飞船最近已经<a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/4/14/8406063/spacex-falcon-9-barge-landing-attempt-fails\" target=\"_blank\">第 </a></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/4/14/8406063/spacex-falcon-9-barge-landing-attempt-fails\" target=\"_blank\">N </a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.theverge.com/2015/4/14/8406063/spacex-falcon-9-barge-landing-attempt-fails\" target=\"_blank\">次回收失败</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">了，但在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Musk </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的带动下，私人公司进入太空领域渐渐成了一件时髦的事情，昨天<a href=\"http://qdaily.com/display/articles/8593.html\" target=\"_blank\">《好奇心日报》就报道</a>了</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">私人公司 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Rocket Lab </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">要造电动火箭的消息。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t事实上，向近地轨道发射火箭和卫星开始变成一门越来越火爆的生意。不管是波音这样的巨头，还是微软的联合创始人 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Paul Allen </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">以及维珍航空 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">CEO Richard Branson </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">爵士，他们都在涌进这项预估年产值可达 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">19 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">亿美元的产业。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://media.gotraffic.net/images/iicUwP5i7Cdo/v3/750x-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><em>近十年每年卫星发射的数量（图片来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-04-13/forget-musk-s-mars-billionaires-branson-allen-seek-earth-orbit\" target=\"_blank\"><em>彭博社</em></a><em>）</em><em></em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t据咨询公司 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Teal Group </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的数据，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2014 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年发射的卫星达到了 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">303 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">颗，是以往年份的近两倍，且仍有价值近 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">亿美元的商用卫星发射还在排队等候。而 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2011 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年才成立的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\"><a href=\"http://www.generationorbit.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Generation Orbit </a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.generationorbit.com/\" target=\"_blank\">卫星发射服务公司</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">COO Piplica </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">称他们今年收到了 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">10 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">封意向书，预计每年将发射 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">200 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">到 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">250 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">颗卫星。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\tTeal Group <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的太空研究负责人 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Marco Caceres </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在<a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-04-13/forget-musk-s-mars-billionaires-branson-allen-seek-earth-orbit\" target=\"_blank\">接受彭博社采访时称</a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：“这是未来的趋势，哪怕有人说我们将看到一年发射几千颗卫星，这也不是什么疯话。”</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t更重要的是卫星发射的成本也在下降，原先美国公司用俄罗斯的第聂伯号（<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Dnepr</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）运载火箭“搭便车”发射商业卫星的费用是 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">1200 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万美元，而且还得按着火箭的发射时间表等候。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\tRocket Lab <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">研发的轻型火箭兴许能在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2016 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年让发射收费降低到 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">490 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万美元，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Generation Orbit </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">则在努力接近 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">200 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万美元，而波音未来的报价更是可能低于 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">100 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万美元。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t为了节约成本，这些公司的新办法层出不穷——当然 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Musk </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">那至今没成功的“回收火箭大法”还是太难。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t“小而美”才省钱\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t如今越来越多被发射上天的商用卫星都是 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万美元左右的小卫星，重量最低的也只有 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">1 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">千克，作用一般是监控农作物、创建互联网热点连接或者追踪天气等。发射这类卫星用大功率运载火箭，实在有点“杀鸡用牛刀”的即视感，而且这类商用卫星的发射一般是作为大火箭的第二载荷“捎带”上去的，发射时间得根据大火箭的安排来，往往一等就是一两年。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t为此，目前大部分商业卫星发射公司都在开发轻型火箭。<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Rocket Lab </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的火箭只有 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">18 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">米高，是俄罗斯第聂伯号火箭的一半。而且 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Rocket Lab </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">也放弃在佛罗里达州肯尼迪航天中心发射火箭，而是选在南半球的新西兰，可选的轨道角度更大，同时——也更便宜。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t当然还有更小的火箭，不过这就不是在地上发射的了。</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>\r\n\t 与其回收，不如从飞机上发射火箭\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t用飞机发射火箭则是波音、<span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Generation Orbit </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">等公司能做到更低价的法宝。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">飞机上发射的都是更小型的火箭，比如波音公司正在研发的用于飞机上发射的火箭只有 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">7 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">米多一点点高，这严格说来只能算是火箭的最后一节。</span>它的省钱原理其实和火箭回收类似，毕竟发射火箭的飞机可以多次使用，就相当于回收了正常火箭的前几级。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t和地面发射后再回收相比，飞机发射的技术难度会小很多。这其实和发射一枚导弹一样，像波音公司用的飞机就是 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">F-15E </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">战斗机；当然战斗机也不是所有公司都买得到，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Generation Orbit 则</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">使用了湾流</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">公司</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Gulfstream</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">生产的“湾流”客机。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5c/Lockheed_TriStar_launches_Pegasus_with_Space_Technology_5.jpg/800px-Lockheed_TriStar_launches_Pegasus_with_Space_Technology_5.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><em>用湾流客机发射</em><span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><em>小型火箭</em></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t此外，微软联合创始人 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Paul Allen </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">也成立了 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Stratolaunch </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">项目研究在平流层发射火箭的技术。昨日，</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Allen </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Vulcan </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">集团<a href=\"http://www.space.com/29117-vulcan-aerospace-paul-allen-private-spaceflight.html\" target=\"_blank\">又宣布</a></span><a href=\"http://www.space.com/29117-vulcan-aerospace-paul-allen-private-spaceflight.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">成立新的 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Vulcan Aerospace </span></a><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.space.com/29117-vulcan-aerospace-paul-allen-private-spaceflight.html\" target=\"_blank\">公司</a>，计划制造世界上最大的飞机用于发射火箭。新飞机的翼展将达到 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">117 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">米，比空客 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">A380 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">还长 37 米</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，拥有 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">6 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个引擎，预计会在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2016 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年进入测试阶段。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t维珍航空 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">CEO Richard Branson </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">创立的维珍银河（</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Virgin Galactic</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）则会使用自己制造的“火箭飞机”：“白骑士 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号”（</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">WhiteKnightTwo</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">），它个体比 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">Stratolaunch </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的小，也只有 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">4 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个引擎。</span></p>\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6a/WhiteKnight_Two_flying.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em>白骑士 2 号</em><em>，图片来自：</em><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scaled_Composites_White_Knight_Two\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Wikipedia</em></a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t但“白骑士 <span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号”</span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2014 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年就已投入使用，搭载过“太空船 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号”以测试未来的豪华太空游。不过在那次试验中，“太空船 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号”分离不久便坠毁，导致一名飞行员不幸丧生。进入卫星发射领域后，</span><span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">预计</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">“白骑士 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号”将在 </span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman';\">2016 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年测试全新的发射技术。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Launch_vehicle\" target=\"_blank\">Wikipedia</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p></p>\r\n\n\n\n"}